# ==============================================================================
# SlopGuesser Client — Environment Variables
# ==============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values for your environment.
# All variables are optional with sensible defaults for local development.
#
# Vite exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the client bundle.
# See: https://vitejs.dev/guide/env-and-mode.html
# ==============================================================================

# --- API Configuration ---

# Base URL for API requests. In development, the Vite dev server proxies
# /api requests to the backend automatically (see vite.config.ts).
# In production, nginx handles the proxy (see nginx.conf).
# Only set this if you need to override the default proxy behavior.
# Example: https://api.slopguesser.com
# Default: (empty — uses relative /api paths with proxy)
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
